snippet.textDisplay:
Being conpletely honest i'm the student who does their homework as soon as i get it. If i have a break at school, i start my homework there and that way i get lots of free time and get to do things i want. At home, i start studying as soon as i get home so im always the first done in my class which is a selective class.
I can give some tips, what i always have with me is:
The books i need
Milk tea
Good music (i have a studying playlist)
Highlighters
Laptop
Pens

Remember to take breaks with small snacks, not your phone! You'll get distracted that way
